[Enable Difficulty Select (ASM) ]
author=RyTheHexer
description=In the NTSC-J release of the game, there exists the typical RE difficulty selection on starting a new game. This is missing in NTSC-U and PAL versions. This code restores this feature. The options are: normal (the default one), easy and very easy (read: very VERY easy!) 
