[Freeze Enemies/NPCs [ASM]]
author=RyTheHexer
description=NOTE! This could easily break stuff. I recommend turning this code off when not needed, and certainly between area transitions as it can break game logic/events. Save often and also use savestates (emulator users.)

It works by completely bypassing a large portion of game code controlling NPC movement/animations. 
patch=1,EE,20174A90,extended,03E00008
patch=1,EE,20170A94,extended,00000000

[Freeze Timers (ASM)]
author=RyTheHexer
description=Stops a lot of in-game countdown timers. Works during last boss battle too. 
