[Rapid Fire [ASM]]
author=RyTheHexer
description=Code provided to fill pending request from many years ago. I've ported my PAL version code to NTSC. 

This works for all weapons, removing the delay between shots. Best combined with inf ammo / no reload codes. 
patch=1,EE,0014416F,extended,0000008C

