[Walk Through Walls (R2 Up On/R2 Down Off)]
author=47iscool
description=1. You can also walk through fire without getting hurt
2. Zombies can also walk through walls
patch=1,EE,E002FDEF,extended,01E0DBC2
patch=1,EE,2025E930,extended,03E00008
patch=1,EE,2025E934,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,E002FDBF,extended,01E0DBC2
patch=1,EE,2025E930,extended,27BDFE90
patch=1,EE,2025E934,extended,7FBF00C0

[Walk Through Walls OFF]
author=bungholio
description=It's better with a joker command because it either stays on or off and doesn't mess with other things.
patch=1,EE,20432308,extended,00000000

[Walk Through Walls ON]
author=bungholio
description=It's better with a joker command because it either stays on or off and doesn't mess with other things.
patch=1,EE,20432308,extended,FFFFFFFF

[Walk Through Walls [With Side Effects; Use With Joker]]
author=bungholio
description=10 - As long as this is set, you can&#039;t walk through walls, so never turn this on.
01 - If this bit isn&#039;t set, your lighter will never emit light if it&#039;s equipped while you walk through walls.
02 - Enemies can&#039;t grab you, you can&#039;t access start menu or map or maybe other menus since I didn&#039;t check them all, can&#039;t active cutscenes (I skipped by the explosion in the beginning of the game and skipped by Steve too), can&#039;t pick up items, and probably more side effects, but you can walk through walls. Good with a joker though.
04 - Identical to 02, except enemies don&#039;t attempt to grab you. Once they are within grab range they stop in place, then they grab after you disable this.
80 - Never activate this, freezes the game.
patch=1,EE,004322E0,extended,00000010